<div id="outline-container-org30cd4b1" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org30cd4b1"><span class="section-number-3">8.2</span> Number of Verses of Surah-Juz-Hizb-RubUlHizb-PageNumber</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-8-2">
<p>
These will give, not the <b>list</b> of verses, but the <b>number</b> of verses of various units.
</p>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-orgb3f3566" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orgb3f3566"><span class="section-number-4">8.2.1</span> give-the-number-of-verses-of-surah.sh</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-8-2-1">
<p>
Shows the <b>number</b> of verses that belong to a particular Sûrah.
</p>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-org55a6fe8" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org55a6fe8"><span class="section-number-4">8.2.2</span> show-number-of-verses-that-belong-to-this-juz.sh</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-8-2-2">
<p>
Shows the <b>number</b> of verses that belong to a particular Juz.
</p>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-org9f86cc0" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org9f86cc0"><span class="section-number-4">8.2.3</span> show-number-of-verses-that-belong-to-this-hizb.sh</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-8-2-3">
<p>
Shows the <b>number</b> of verses that belong to a particular Ḥizb.
</p>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-orgd82772f" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orgd82772f"><span class="section-number-4">8.2.4</span> show-number-of-verses-that-belong-to-this-rub-al-hizb.sh</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-8-2-4">
<p>
Shows the <b>number</b> of verses that belong to a particular Rub-`ul-Ḥizb.
</p>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-org0141f19" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org0141f19"><span class="section-number-4">8.2.5</span> show-number-of-verses-that-belong-to-this-page-number.sh</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-8-2-5">
<p>
Shows the <b>number</b> of verses that belong to a particular page.
</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-orga1e9a0d" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="orga1e9a0d"><span class="section-number-3">8.3</span> Show ID of the Greater Unit to Which a Verse Belongs</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-8-3">
<p>
This will show the <b>number</b> (name) of the upper unit to which a verse belongs.
</p>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-org5758f2f" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org5758f2f"><span class="section-number-4">8.3.1</span> show-juz-to-which-this-ayah-belongs.sh</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-8-3-1">
<p>
It takes one ayah and returns the <b>number</b> of the Juz to which it belongs. For instance if given the value <code>002159</code>, it returns: <code>02</code>, which means: the ayah belongs to Juz N°02 of the Quran.
</p>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-org41278b1" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org41278b1"><span class="section-number-4">8.3.2</span> show-hizb-to-which-this-ayah-belongs.sh</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-8-3-2">
<p>
It takes one ayah and returns the <b>number</b> of the Ḥizb to which it belongs. For instance if given the value <code>001007</code>, it returns: <code>01</code>, which means: the ayah belongs to Ḥizb N°01 of the Quran.
</p>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-org5dcf35e" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org5dcf35e"><span class="section-number-4">8.3.3</span> show-rub-al-hizb-to-which-this-ayah-belongs.sh</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-8-3-3">
<p>
It takes one ayah and returns the <b>number</b> of the Rub-`ul-Ḥizb to which it belongs. For instance if given the value <code>114006</code>, returns: <code>240</code>, which means: the ayah belongs to Rub-`ul-Ḥizb N°240 of the Quran.
</p>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-orgfb78ea4" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orgfb78ea4"><span class="section-number-4">8.3.4</span> show-page-number-to-which-this-ayah-belongs.sh</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-8-3-4">
<p>
It takes one ayah and returns the <b>number</b> of the Page to which it belongs. For instance if given the value <code>002285</code>, returns: <code>049</code>, which means: the ayah belongs to Page N°049 of the Quran.
</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-orga5ec480" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="orga5ec480"><span class="section-number-3">8.4</span> Show Some More Info for a Surah</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-8-4">
<p>
The following functions take one ayah_id and return some information about the Sûrah to which it belongs.
</p>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-orgea4605f" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orgea4605f"><span class="section-number-4">8.4.1</span> show-surah-meccan-or-medinan.sh</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-8-4-1">
<p>
Shows whether the Sûrah to which this ayah belongs is Meccan or Medinan.
</p>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-org108a42e" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org108a42e"><span class="section-number-4">8.4.2</span> show-surah-name-arabic.sh</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-8-4-2">
<p>
Shows the Arabic Name of the Sûrah to which this ayah belongs.
</p>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-orgbe99525" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orgbe99525"><span class="section-number-4">8.4.3</span> show-surah-name-english.sh</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-8-4-3">
<p>
Shows the English Name of the Sûrah to which this ayah belongs.
</p>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-org62a6e12" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org62a6e12"><span class="section-number-4">8.4.4</span> show-surah-number.sh</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-8-4-4">
<p>
Shows the 3-digit Number of the Sûrah to which this ayah belongs.
</p>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-orge55f8b0" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orge55f8b0"><span class="section-number-4">8.4.5</span> show-surah-number-without-leading-zeros.sh</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-8-4-5">
<p>
Shows the 3-digit Number of the Sûrah to which this ayah belongs, without leading zeros. This means, for instance, that where the above script would return <code>006</code>, this one returns <code>6</code>. This is sometimes useful for some particular purposes.
</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-orga010f27" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="orga010f27"><span class="section-number-3">8.5</span> Show Number of Elements Contained in the Unit to Which a Verse Belongs</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-8-5">
<p>
This take a single ayah_id and returns the number of elements contained the greater unit to which it belongs.
</p>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-org64ca5f3" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org64ca5f3"><span class="section-number-4">8.5.1</span> get-number-of-ayaat-of-the-surah-to-which-this-ayah-belongs.sh</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-8-5-1">
<p>
Returns the number of verses of the Sûrah to which a given ayah belongs.
</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-org043fafc" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org043fafc"><span class="section-number-3">8.6</span> Other Ayah Related BASH Functions</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-8-6">
</div>
<div id="outline-container-org242e568" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org242e568"><span class="section-number-4">8.6.1</span> <code>show_number_of_pages_of_a_surah.sh</code></h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-8-6-1">
<p>
This program take one verse id (i.e., 002008) and returns the following:
</p>

<ul class="org-ul">
<li>The Total Pages of the Sûrah</li>
<li>The Page on which is located the entered verse id</li>
<li>The the pages that come before the entered verse id</li>
<li>And the number of the Remaining pages in the Sūrah</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-orgdc14a5d" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="orgdc14a5d"><span class="section-number-4">8.6.2</span> ayah-necessitates-sadjdah-or-not.sh</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-8-6-2">
<p>
This tells us wether a given verse necessitates prosternation after recitation or not.
</p>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-org6d9afb4" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="org6d9afb4"><span class="section-number-4">8.6.3</span> play-basmala-for-the-113-suwar.sh</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-8-6-3">
<p>
This program is able to know when the user is playing the first verses of the 113 chapters of the Quran for which it is mandatory to read the Basmalah and it consequently plays it.
</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>


