</p>

<p>
<a href="programs/uncompressed/Show_Surah_Metadata/Number_of_Verses_of_Surah-Juz-Hizb-RubUlHizb-PageNumber/show-number-of-verses-that-belong-to-this-page-number.sh">show-number-of-verses-that-belong-to-this-page-number.sh</a>
</p>

<p>
<a href="programs/uncompressed/Show_Surah_Metadata/Number_of_Verses_of_Surah-Juz-Hizb-RubUlHizb-PageNumber/show-number-of-verses-that-belong-to-this-rub-al-hizb.sh">show-number-of-verses-that-belong-to-this-rub-al-hizb.sh</a>
