<div id="outline-container-org3b69689" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="org3b69689"><span class="section-number-3">9.10</span> Custom Tanzil/Zekr Translation/Tafsir Files</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-9-10">
<p>
These are a set of Tanzil/Zekr translation or Tafsir files that I prepared for my personal use over the years. In the past years I did my best to get in touch with the Tanzil project in order to send them these files for the benefit of other people but they wouldn't answer my emails. In the end I got frustrated and stopped sending them emails. Here I am today, after many years, publishing them on the internet myself. All praise is due to Allah, The Lord of the Worlds. <br />
</p>


<p>
<b>Arabic Tafasir of the Quran</b>:
</p>
<ol class="org-ol">
<li><a href="downloads/zekr-extras-tafasir/ar.baghawy.trans.zip">ar.baghawy.trans.zip</a>     <b>Tafsir Al-Baghawiy</b></li>

<li><a href="downloads/zekr-extras-tafasir/ar.e3rab.trans.zip">ar.e3rab.trans.zip</a>       <b>I'raab-ul-Quran</b></li>

<li><a href="downloads/zekr-extras-tafasir/ar.jalalayn.trans.zip">ar.jalalayn.trans.zip</a>    <b>Tafsir Jallalayn</b></li>

<li><a href="downloads/zekr-extras-tafasir/ar.katheer.trans.zip">ar.katheer.trans.zip</a>     <b>Tafsir Ibn Katheer</b></li>

<li><a href="downloads/zekr-extras-tafasir/ar.muyassar.trans.zip">ar.muyassar.trans.zip</a>    <b>Tafsir al-Muyassar</b></li>

<li><a href="downloads/zekr-extras-tafasir/ar.qortoby.trans.zip">ar.qortoby.trans.zip</a>     <b>Tafsir al-Qurṭubi</b></li>

<li><a href="downloads/zekr-extras-tafasir/ar.sa3dy.trans.zip">ar.sa3dy.trans.zip</a>       <b>Tafsir as-Sa`adi</b></li>

<li><a href="downloads/zekr-extras-tafasir/ar.tabary.trans.zip">ar.tabary.trans.zip</a>      <b>Tafsir aṭ-Ṭabari</b></li>

<li><a href="downloads/zekr-extras-tafasir/ar.tanweer.trans.zip">ar.tanweer.trans.zip</a>     <b>Tanwir al-Miqbas Tafsir</b></li>

<li><a href="downloads/zekr-extras-tafasir/ar.waseet.trans.zip">ar.waseet.trans.zip</a>     <b>Tafsir Waseet</b></li>
</ol>



